 trong <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">nh√≥m Slack</a>.<br />\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-234 size-full\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2017/09/wp-gutenberg-preview.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2017/09/wp-gutenberg-preview.png 640w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2017/09/wp-gutenberg-preview-300x122.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></p>\n<h2>Ti·∫øp t·ª•c ph√°t tri·ªÉn tr√¨nh so·∫°n th·∫£o m·ªõi</h2>\n<p>Trong v√†i th√°ng nay, ƒë·ªôi core v·∫´n ƒëang l√†m vi·ªác tr√™n Gutenberg, tr√¨nh so·∫°n th·∫£o m·ªõi cho WordPress core. Trong khi Gutenberg v·∫´n ƒëang ƒë∆∞·ª£c ph√°t tri·ªÉn v√† v·∫´n c√≤n ph·∫£i t·ªën nhi·ªÅu th·ªùi gian tr∆∞·ªõc khi s·∫µn s√†ng, nhi·ªÅu c·∫£i ti·∫øn ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c th√™m v√†o. Th·ª±c t·∫ø, <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2017/08/29/whats-new-in-gutenberg-august-29/\">v1.0.0 c·ªßa Gutenberg</a> ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ph√°t h√†nh trong tu·∫ßn n√†y.</p>\n<p>Tr√¨nh so·∫°n th·∫£o m·ªõi ƒë√£ c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·∫£i v·ªÅ <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/test/handbook/call-for-testing/gutenberg-testing/\">d√πng th·ª≠ nh∆∞ m·ªôt plugin</a> v√† <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2017/08/11/revised-suggested-roadmap-for-gutenberg-and-customization/\">k·∫ø ho·∫°ch ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªÅ ra</a> l√† s·∫Ω nh·∫≠p chung tr√¨nh so·∫°n th·∫£o n√†y v√†o core v√†o ƒë·∫ßu nƒÉm 2018. B·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ tham gia v√†o vi·ªác ph√°t tri·ªÉn Gutenberg b·∫±ng c√°ch tham gia k√™nh #core-editor trong <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">nh√≥m Slack</a> v√† theo d√µi <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/\">blog ph√°t tri·ªÉn c·ªßa nh√≥m WordPress Core</a>.</p>\n<h2>ƒê·ªçc th√™m:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Trong ch·ªß ƒë·ªÅ Gutenberg, <a href=\"https://ma.tt/2017/08/we-called-it-gutenberg-for-a-reason/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Matt Mullenweg</a> ƒë√£ c√≥ m·ªôt b√†i vi·∫øt nh√¨n nh·∫≠n c√°c v·∫•n ƒë·ªÅ m√† c·ªông ƒë·ªìng ƒë√£ ph·∫£n √°nh v·ªÅ c√¥ng c·ª• so·