ªùi ƒë√≥ng g√≥p m·ªõi v·∫´n lu√¥n l√† v·∫•n ƒë·ªÅ nh·ª©c nh·ªëi cho h·∫ßu h·∫øt c√°c team Trong khi c√°c team ƒë·ªÅu nhi·ªát t√¨nh ch√†o ƒë√≥n c√°c contributor, ƒë√¥i khi r·∫•t kh√≥ cho nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi m·ªõi c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c c√°ch tham gia.</p>\n<p>Th√°ng n√†y, ƒë·ªôi Core ƒë√£ th·ª±c hi·ªán m·ªôt v√†i s√°ng ki·∫øn m·ªõi tuy·ªát v·ªùi: <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2017/06/30/announcing-a-weekly-new-contributors-meeting/\">h·ªçp m·∫∑t m·ªói tu·∫ßn d√†nh cho nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë√≥ng g√≥p m·ªõi</a> nh∆∞ l√† m·ªôt c√°ch ƒë·ªÉ khuy·∫øn kh√≠ch s·ª± tham gia v√† t·∫°o ra nh·ªØng ƒë√≥ng g√≥p m·ªõi m·∫ª. Nh·ªØng cu·ªôc h·ªçp kh√¥ng ch·ªâ ch√∫ tr·ªçng v√†o c√°c l·ªói (bug) ph√π h·ª£p cho nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë√≥ng g√≥p l·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu, n√≥ c√≤n t·∫°o kh√¥ng gian cho nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë√≥ng g√≥p gi√†u kinh nghi·ªám gi√∫p ƒë·ª° nh·ªØng c√° nh√¢n c√≤n m·ªõi trong vi·ªác ph√°t tri·ªÉn WordPress core.</p>\n<p>Cu·ªôc h·ªçp ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·ªï ch·ª©c Th·ª© T∆∞ h√†ng tu·∫ßn v√†o 19:00 UTC trong k√™nh #core trong <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">nh√≥m Slack Making WordPress</a>.</p>\n<h2>TƒÉng c∆∞·ªùng t·∫≠p trung v√†o c√°c PHP practices trong WordPress core</h2>\n<p>Nh·∫±m gi√∫p m·ªçi ng∆∞·ªùi c√πng nhau ph√°t tri·ªÉn WordPress core, m·ªôt k√™nh m·ªõi trong <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">nh√≥m Slack Making WordPress</a> t√™n l√† #core-php ƒë∆∞·ª£c thi·∫øt k·∫ø ƒë·ªÉ t·∫≠p trung v√†o vi·ªác ph√°t tri·ªÉn PHP trong d·ª± √°n.</p>\n<p>C√πng v·ªõi s·ª± t·∫≠p trung n√¢ng cao v√†o PHP, m·ªôt <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2017/07/06/announcement-for-weekly-php-meetings/\">cu·ªôc h·ªçp h√†ng tu·∫ßn m·ªõi ƒëang ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·ªï ch·ª©c</a> v√†o m·ªói Th·ª© Hai v√†o 18:00 UTC trong #core-php ƒë·ªÉ n√¢ng cao k·ªπ nƒÉng PHP trong WordPress core.</p>\n<h2>TƒÉng m·∫°nh s·ªë l∆∞·ª£ng c√°c meetup</h2>\n<p>Widget s·ª± ki·ªán trong b·∫£ng ƒëi·ªÅu khi·ªÉn trong WordPress 4.8 hi·ªÉn th·ªã c√°c s·ª± ki·ªán WordPress xung quanh s·∫Øp di·ªÖn ra cho ng∆∞·ªùi d√πng ƒë√£ ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p. Nh·ªØng s·ª± ki·ªán ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒëƒÉng trong widget n√†y ƒë∆∞·ª£c l·∫•y t·ª´ <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pro/wordpress/\">ch∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh ch∆∞∆°ng m·ª•c g·∫∑p m·∫∑t</a>, c≈©ng nh∆∞ t·ª´ <a href=\"https://central.wordcamp.org/schedule/\">L·ªãch WordCamp</a>.</p>\n<p>Widget n√†y cung c·∫•p kh·∫£ nƒÉng hi·ªÉn th·ªã l·ªõn h∆°n cho c√°c s·ª± ki·ªán WordPress ch√≠nh th·ª©c, v√† khuy·∫øn kh√≠ch s·ª± tham gia c·ªßa c·ªông ƒë·ªìng trong nh·ªØng s·ª± ki·ªán n√†y. C√≥ th·ªÉ kh·∫≥ng ƒë·ªãnh r·∫±ng widget ƒë√£ ƒë·∫°t ƒë∆∞·ª£c m·ª•c ƒë√≠ch m·ªôt c√°ch ƒë√°ng kh√¢m ph·ª•c ‚Äî k·ªÉ t·ª´ khi WordPress 4.8 ƒë∆∞·ª£c ph√°t h√†nh kho·∫£ng h∆°n m·ªôt th√°ng tr∆∞·ªõc, 31 meetup m·ªõi ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c h√¨nh th√†nh v·ªõi 15.647 th√†nh vi√™n m·ªõi xuy√™n su·ªët c·∫£ ch∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh. Ch√∫ng ta c√≥ th·ªÉ so s√°nh v·ªõi 19 meetup m·ªõi v√† ch·ªâ 7.071 th√†nh vi√™n m·ªõi trong c√πng m·ªôt th·ªùi ƒëi·ªÉm nƒÉm ngo√°i.</p>\n<p>B·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m th·∫•y m·ªôt meetup xung quanh ƒë·ªÉ tham gia <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pro/wordpress/\">tr√™n meetup.com</a>, v√† n·∫øu b·∫°n mu·ªën tham gia t·ªï ch·ª©c s·ª± ki·ªán cho c·ªông ƒë·ªìng c·ªßa b·∫°n, b·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ xem th√™m v·ªÅ ch∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh n√†y <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community/meetups/\">tr√™n trang ƒê·ªôi C·ªông ƒë·ªìng</a> ho·∫∑c b·∫±ng c√°ch tham gia k√™nh #community-events tr√™n <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">nh√≥m Slack Making WordPress</a>.</p>\n<h2>WordPress 4.8.1 s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c ra m·∫Øt s·ªõm</h2>\n<p>B·∫£n b·∫£o tr√¨ ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n c·ªßa WordPress 4.8 s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c ph√°t h√†nh v√†o tu·∫ßn t·ªõi, sau khi 4.8 ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ph√°t h√†nh h∆°n m·ªôt th√°ng. B·∫£n ra m·∫Øt n√†y s·ª≠a m·ªôt v√†i l·ªói quan tr·ªçng trong WordPress core v√† h·∫ßu h·∫øt c√°c ng∆∞·ªùi d√πng s·∫Ω th·∫•y trang web c·ªßa h·ªç t·ª± ƒë·ªông c·∫≠p nh·∫≠t l√™n b·∫£n n√†y.</p>\n<p>N·∫øu b·∫°n mu·ªën gi√∫p ƒë·ª° b·∫±ng c√°ch d√πng th·ª≠ phi√™n b·∫£n n√†y tr∆∞·ªõc khi n√≥ ph√°t h√†nh, b·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ theo d√µi <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/handbook/testing/beta/\">h∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n th·ª≠ nghi·ªám b·∫£n beta</a> cho WordPress core. ƒê·ªÉ ƒë√≥ng g√≥p trong vi·ªác x√¢y d·ª±ng WordPress core, h√£y tham gia k√™nh #core trong <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">nh√≥m Slack Making WordPress</a>, v√† theo d√µi <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/\">blog c·ªßa ƒë·ªôi Core</a>.</p>\n<h2>ƒê·ªçc th√™m:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>C√°c ·ª©ng d·ª•ng WordPress tr√™n di ƒë·ªông ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c c·∫≠p nh·∫≠t v·ªõi <a href=\"https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2017/07/24/a-brand-new-editor-for-the-wordpress-mobile-apps/\">c√¥ng c·ª• ch·ªânh s·ª≠a text m·ªõi</a>.</li>\n<li>ƒê·ªÉ khuy·∫øn kh√≠ch c√°c ng∆∞·ªùi d√πng WordPress n√¢ng c·∫•p phi√™n b·∫£n PHP c·ªßa h·ªç, hai t√≠nh nƒÉng ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªÅ xu·∫•t &#8211; m·ªôt <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/41191\">ƒë·ªÉ cung c·∫•p th√¥ng b√°o ƒë·∫øn ng∆∞·ªùi d√πng</a> v√† m·ªôt ƒë·ªÉ <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/40934\">cho ph√©p xu·∫•t hi·ªán c√°c y√™u c·∫ßu phi√™n b·∫£n PHP ƒë∆∞·ª£c x√°c ƒë·ªãnh b·ªüi plugin v√† theme</a>.</li>\n<li>John Maeda vi·∫øt <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/design/2017/07/14/whywordpress2/\">m·ªôt b√†i vi·∫øt tuy·ªát v·ªùi</a> v·ªÅ s·ª± t·ª± do m√† WordPress mang l·∫°i.</li>\n<li>Gutenberg, c√¥ng c·ª• ch·ªânh s·ª≠a m·ªõi cho WordPress, v·∫´n <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2017/07/28/whats-new-in-gutenberg-28th-july/\">trong qu√° tr√¨nh ti·∫øp t·ª•c ph√°t tri·ªÉn</a> ‚Äî m·ªçi ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë·ªÅu ƒë∆∞·ª£c m·ªùi <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/test/handbook/call-for-testing/gutenberg-testing/\">d√πng th·ª≠</a>.</li>\n<li>ƒê·ªôi Meta WordPress ƒëang b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/meta/2017/07/26/experiment-wordcamp-org-bug-scrubs/\">m·ªôt s√°ng ki·∫øn m·ªõi</a> ƒë∆∞a c·ªông ƒë·ªìng ƒë·∫øn v·ªõi nhau ƒë·ªÉ c√πng t·∫≠p trung s·ª≠a l·ªói xuy√™n su·ªët m·∫°ng l∆∞·ªõi WordCamp.org.</li>\n<li>WordCamp US ƒëang <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/meta/2017/07/26/experiment